// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/4cjyWz transparent voxels painters algorithm, 2021 by jt
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/7stXzn Voxel Raycast with Sub-Objects

// Visualization of transparent voxels:
// Find intersection of ray with bounding box,
// then traverse voxels back-to-front to use painter's algorithm for compositing.

// tags: raytracing, transparency, raycasting, voxel, volumetric, transparent, dda, algorithm, opacity, reverse, painters, backtofront

